'''羅薩奧蒂卡'''集團（{{lang-en|Luxottica Group S.p.A.}}），或譯'''陆逊梯卡'''，是全球最大的[[太陽眼鏡|太陽眼鏡]]公司。

==历史==
於1961年在[[意大利|意大利]]成立，市場佔有率愈80%<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/21/business/21glasses.html?ref=luxotticagroupspa |title=Luxottica to Buy a U.S. Sunglasses Maker |work=in The New York Times June 21, 2007 |date=2007-06-21 |accessdate=2015-08-16 |archive-date=2017-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814095740/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/06/21/business/21glasses.html?ref=luxotticagroupspa |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/deancrutchfield/2012/11/27/luxottica-sees-itself-as-king-raising-questions-about-brand-authenticity/ | title=Luxottica Sees Itself As King, Raising Questions About Brand Authenticity | date=November 27, 2012 | work=Forbes | first=Dean | last=Crutchfield | accessdate=2015-08-16 | archive-date=2020-11-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113164349/https://www.forbes.com/sites/deancrutchfield/2012/11/27/luxottica-sees-itself-as-king-raising-questions-about-brand-authenticity/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[垂直整合|垂直整合]]了整個[[供應鏈|供應鏈]]，業務涵蓋了生產、批發和零售，旗下品牌包括：[[亮視點|亮視點]]、[[雷朋|雷朋]]、[[Oakley|Oakley]]和奢侈品牌如[[香奈兒|香奈兒]]、[[普拉達|普拉達]]、[[亞曼尼|亞曼尼]]、[[巴寶莉|巴寶莉]]、[[凡賽斯|凡賽斯]]的太陽眼鏡業務。

2017年1月17日，羅薩奧蒂卡宣佈將和法國鏡片制造商[[依視路|依視路]]合併，2018年10月1日，新公司[[EssilorLuxottica|EssilorLuxottica]]成立。

